            "code": "import pandas as pd\n\n# Load the CSV file\nfile_path = '/mnt/data/assistant-Qca4GeCRHckCLZFgKeyvkV-synthetic_500_quarterly_results.csv'\ndata = pd.read_csv(file_path)\n\n# Display the first few rows of the dataframe\ndata.head()",
